xorcist]]''\n*''[[Exorcist II: The Heretic]]''\n*''[[Attack of the 50 Foot Woman]]''\n*''[[Donovan's Brain (film)|Donovan's Brain]]''\n*''[[Predator (film)|Predator]]''\n*''[[Slaughter High]]''\n*''[[Man's Best Friend (1993 film)|Man's Best Friend]]''\n*''[[Mad Max 2]]''\n*''[[The Doberman Gang]]''\n*''[[The Elephant Man (film)|The Elephant Man]]''\n*''[[Alien (film)|Alien]]''\n*''[[It! The Terror from Beyond Space]]''\n*''[[Razorback (film)|Razorback]]''\n*''[[Mothra vs. Godzilla|Godzilla vs. Mothra]]''\n*''[[Invasion of Astro-Monster|Godzilla vs. Monster Zero]]''\n*''[[Megaforce]]''\n*''[[Time Runner]]''\n*''[[The Protector (1985 film)|The Protector]]''\n*''[[The Warriors (film)|The Warriors]]''\n*''[[Skeeter (film)|Skeeter]]''\n*''[[Endangered Species (1982 film)|Endangered Species]]'' \n*''[[It's Alive III: Island of the Alive]]''\n*''[[Look What's Happened to Rosemary's Baby]]''\n*''[[When Dinosaurs Ruled the Earth]]''\n*''[[Howard the Duck (film)|Howard the Duck]]''\n*''[[Return of the Living Dead Part II]]''\n*''[[Frankenstein (1992 film)|Frankenstein]]''\n*''[[The Nutty Professor (1996 film)|The Nutty Professor]]''\n*''[[Sleepstalker]]''\n*''[[Philadelphia Experiment II]]''\n*''[[Alien 3]]''\n*''[[Barbarella (film)|Barbarella]]''\n*''[[Steel Dawn]]''\n*''[[The Serpent and the Rainbow (film)|The Serpent and the Rainbow]]''\n*''[[Ghoulies]]''\n*''[[The Birds (film)|The Birds]]''\n*''[[Troll (film)|Troll]]''\n*''[[Trancers]]''\n*''[[Phantasm II]]''\n*''[[Big Trouble in Little China]]''\n*''[[Theodore Rex (film)|Theodore Rex]]''\n*''[[Wes Craven's New Nightmare]]''\n*''[[Halloween II (1981 film)|Halloween II]]''\n*''[[Conan The Destroyer]]''\n*''[[Hercules in New York]]''\n*''[[Twilight Zone: The Movie]]''\n*''[[They Live]]''\n*''[[Capricorn One]]''\n*''[[Four Days in November]]''\n*''[[Leviathan (1989 film)|Leviathan]]''\n*''[[Communion (1989 film)|Communion]]''\n*''[[Clash of the Titans (1981 film)|Clash of the Titans]]''\n*''[[The NeverEnding Story (film)|The